    <item>
      <title>标普将 Uber 评级上调至投资级，因盈利增长</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-16/uber-raised-to-investment-grade-status-by-s-p-on-earnings-growth</link>
      <description><![CDATA[标准普尔全球评级周五将优步科技公司的信用评级上调至投资级，理由是这家叫车和送餐公司的盈利持续增长。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-16/uber-raised-to-investment-grade-status-by-s-p-on-earnings-growth</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 16 Aug 2024 22:00:16 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>焦点芯片和 Epic Games 的移动店面 | 彭博科技</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-08-16/chips-in-focus-and-epic-games-mobile-storefront-bloomberg-technology</link>
      <description><![CDATA[彭博社的 Caroline Hyde 和 Ed Ludlow 分析了设备制造商应用材料令人失望的预测，而德州仪器则从《CHIPS 法案》中获利。此外，Epic Games 在与苹果和谷歌进行多年的法律纠纷后推出了新的移动商店，而施格兰继承人 Edgar Bronfman Jr. 即将对派拉蒙提出竞争性报价。（来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-08-16/chips-in-focus-and-epic-games-mobile-storefront-bloomberg-technology</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 16 Aug 2024 19:36:03 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
