    <item>
      <title>科技股上涨推动新兴市场股票创四个月来最佳一周表现</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-16/tech-rally-propels-emerging-stocks-to-best-week-in-four-months</link>
      <description><![CDATA[新兴市场股市上涨，因为交易员们对美国经济将能够避免衰退越来越乐观，同时预计美联储将于下个月开始降息，这应该会给风险资产带来新的提振。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-16/tech-rally-propels-emerging-stocks-to-best-week-in-four-months</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 16 Aug 2024 09:12:43 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
